parameters.name: DOY
parameters.description: Day of Year DDD=3 digit day of year (e.g. 053)

parameters.name: UT
parameters.description: Universal Time of day represented as milliseconds after 00:00:00.000

parameters.name: MASS
parameters.description:
Mass number -                              
                                    4 for He+                                 
                                   12 for C+                                  
                                   14 for N+                                  
                                   16 for O+                                  
                                   28 for N2+ and/or CO+                      
                                   30 for NO+                                 
                                   32 for O2+                                 
                                   44 for CO2+

parameters.name: PULSE
parameters.description: Maximum count rate/sec in 12 second interval
